  <brief_title>A 2-Year Study of an Investigational Drug in Obese Patients (0557-011)</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Double-Blind, Randomized, Placebo-Controlled, Multicenter Study to Assess the Safety, Tolerability, and Efficacy of MK0557 in Obese Patients</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Merck Sharp &amp; Dohme Corp.</agency>
